wsdl:definitions.wsdl:documentation: Data Capture Web Service CL2 version 5.08

wsdl:operation.name: GetEmployee
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a data transfer object (EmployeeDTO) for the employee number parameter passed in if found. It returns an empty data transfer object (EmployeeDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: ValidateProver
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a boolean indicating if the prover number passed in is valid or not.

wsdl:operation.name: GetTestReasons
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a list of test reason data transfer objects (TestReasonDTO) for the reason type passed in.

wsdl:operation.name: GetValidatedAcceptanceSampleMeterByInventoryCode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the inventory code and acceptance job number combination passed in if found. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetValidatedAcceptanceSampleMeterByBarcode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the barcode and acceptance job number combination passed in if found. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetValidatedComplianceSampleMeterByInventoryCode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the inventory code passed in if found. The inventory code must be in an open compliance job. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetValidatedComplianceSampleMeterByBarcode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the barcode number passed in if found. The barcode must be in an open compliance job. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetValidatedEvcDeviceByInventoryCode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the inventory code passed in if found. The inventory code must be in an open EVC job. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetMeterDataByInventoryCode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the inventory code passed in if found. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetMeterDataByInventoryCodeAndSerialNumber
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the inventory code and serial number combination passed in if found. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: GetMeterDataByBarcode
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method returns a meter data transfer object (MeterDTO) for the barcode passed in if found. It returns an empty data transfer object (MeterDTO) if not found.

wsdl:operation.name: ParseProverTestFile
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method is used to parse the test file created by the North Bay rotary and turbine provers. The test file is passed in as a string and is returned as a FileAsEntities object to be used by the North Bay Data Capture client application to present the test file data to the user.

wsdl:operation.name: SubmitProdTestResults
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method is used to submit test results data from the Production Snap provers to be saved in the database. A DiaphragmTestResult object is passed in and a string is returned containing a 'success' message for a successful save or an exception message for a unsuccessful save.

wsdl:operation.name: SubmitQADiaphragmTestResults
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method is used to submit test results data from the QA Snap provers to be saved in the database. A DiaphragmTestResult object is passed in and a string is returned containing a 'success' message for a successful save or an exception message for a unsuccessful save.

wsdl:operation.name: SubmitQARotaryTestResults
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method is used to submit test results data from the QA Rotary provers to be saved in the database. A QARunRotaryTestResult object is passed in and a string is returned containing a 'success' message for a successful save or an exception message for a unsuccessful save.

wsdl:operation.name: SubmitQATurbineTestResults
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method is used to submit test results data from the QA Turbine provers to be saved in the database. A QARunTurbineTestResult object is passed in and a string is returned containing a 'success' message for a successful save or an exception message for a unsuccessful save.

wsdl:operation.name: SubmitQAEvcTestResults
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: This method is used to submit test results data from the QA EVC provers to be saved in the database. A list of QARunEvcTestResult objects is passed in and a string is returned containing a 'success' message for a successful save or an exception message for a unsuccessful save.

wsdl:service.name: DCRWebService
wsdl:service.wsdl:documentation: Data Capture Web Service CL2 version 5.08
